Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:46.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não quero que me descubram!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:50.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se descobrirem, vão me matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:51.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:55.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles já sabem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estão fazendo um alvoroço \Ngraças à sua habilidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:05.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Este espelho é a chave para a \Nfuga das forças aliadas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:08.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se eu cumprir minha parte da missão, \Nme devolverão meu coração!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:13.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E então vou dar uma lição \Nem todos eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.94,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,480)}Ei, Mãe {spanish manga 865}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:27.33,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Como está indo tudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.74,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ainda não ouvi o grito dela...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:33.24,Pensante,,0,0,0,,E a Big Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.42,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Exatamente como planejamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:44.10,Pensante,,0,0,0,,O bolo foi destruído e os \NChapéus de Palha estão causando estragos...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:49.52,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Eles também quebraram o \Nretrato de Mãe Carmel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:53.22,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Então, por que Big Mom não gritou?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.72,Pensante,,0,0,0,,O que diabos está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:07.07,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san, me escute, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:10.66,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Big Mom teve muitas \Ncomoções,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.91,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,então ela não focou sua \Nraiva em uma coisa só!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:15.01,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:17.89,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,769)}Se você diz, vamos fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parem o Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não deixem que ele \Nse aproxime da mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:41.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você está no meu caminho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege, maldito...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:01.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Morra, Katakuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:06.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo, Gang Bege?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:12.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então você nos traiu, Bege... {pace line: "Eu sabia que você nos trairia, Bege...", kind of different}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão Peros! {SC835 9:28:56}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:18.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:20.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mate-os agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Caramba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:28.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O homem que pode ver o \Nfuturo quer tudo rápido.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:35.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas eu também posso ver \No futuro de vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:42.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ao imobilizá-los com meu caramelo, \Nvocês morrerão com expressões patéticas em seus rostos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não será de outra forma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:53.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se ao menos tivéssemos \Nos Raid Suits,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,não deixaríamos que \Nfizessem o que querem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Raid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É uma arma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lambida.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:09.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, você queria trazer isso \Npara o casamento do seu filho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:14.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fuja, Reiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não atrapalhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que ele está fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fazendo um escândalo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.38,Pensante,,0,0,0,, Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.32,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Subestimei sua bondade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:06.01,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Você nem mesmo nos abandona.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.40,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Sempre odiei \Nser uma Vinsmoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.32,Pensante,,0,0,0,,...e me senti \Nenvergonhada por isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:14.89,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.06,Pensante,,0,0,0,,...quando te vi adulto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:24.22,Pensante,,0,0,0,,...me senti aliviada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:34.56,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1100)}Porque ainda há princípios \Nmorais em nossa família.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.33,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:47.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A família de Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:09.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não toque nele, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:14.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vá!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:15.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:19.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gosenmai-gawara...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Seiken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Morra, Katakuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou permitir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:22.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,M...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:25.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mãe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:26.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,M...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:36.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.20,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora, cada um fuja por si.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Embora eu saiba que não estão me ouvindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama está ferida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.20,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ela está enfraquecida!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:20.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Alguém pare o Bege e sua turma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:33.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desgraçado, você nos traiu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Adeus, Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.29,Pensante,,0,0,0,, Mãe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:44.42,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:47.55,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Me escute, Mãe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:52.93,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ninguém me escuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:55.26,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ei, Mãe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:57.96,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Para onde você foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.96,Principio,,0,0,0,,As lágrimas de Big Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:09.48,Principio,,0,0,0,,...remontam aos eventos ocorridos há sessenta e três anos em Elbaf, no Novo Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:17.20,Principio,,0,0,0,,Esta é a ilha onde os famosos \Ngigantes, os guerreiros de Elbaf, vivem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos, chegue mais perto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:38.49,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,485)\fad(534,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}CHARLOTTE LINLIN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:38.49,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)\fad(534,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}(CINCO ANOS DE IDADE - HUMANA)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{\an8}Onde estamos?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já te digo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desça primeiro, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:44.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde estamos?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão a algum lugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:13:00.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pai tem trabalho para \Nfazer por aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:02.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin, você poderia ser uma \Nboa menina e nos esperar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:03.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou com vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:09.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Em troca, você pode comer todos \Nos doces da bolsa que quiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, é isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Todos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então eu espero, espero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou esperar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tchau!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Voltem logo, tá?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:29.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não chore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:35.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Depois de causar tanto estrago, \Nela teve sorte de apenas ser exilada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...não pode ser controlada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Dizem que a Santa Mãe vive aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com certeza ela salvará Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Zarpem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estes mares são perigosos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:58.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Até logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que peixes grandes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que estranho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como demoram.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou com fome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mamãe, papai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para onde foram?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:26.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que ainda não voltaram?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.86,Principio,,0,0,0,,Falando de Elbaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:39.55,Principio,,0,0,0,,foi o lar de guerreiros gigantes, \Nque eram temidos por todo o mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.82,Principio,,0,0,0,,Eles eram chamados de Piratas Gigantes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:50.06,Principio,,0,0,0,,Viajaram por todos os mares e \Nqueimaram incontáveis cidades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:52.52,Principio,,0,0,0,,No entanto,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:57.74,Principio,,0,0,0,,certo dia, de repente, os Piratas Gigantes \Nperderam seus dois capitães...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.72,Principio,,0,0,0,,...e se tornaram uma lenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.42,Principio,,0,0,0,,Depois de perderem seus líderes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:04.26,Principio,,0,0,0,,alguns de seus membros se descuidaram,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:08.08,Principio,,0,0,0,,foram capturados pela Marinha \Ne estavam prestes a ser executados.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Matem-nos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esperem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parem a execução!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os céus exigem uma reconciliação!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:31.51,Principio,,0,0,0,,Apareceu uma bela freira \Nque estava de passagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:35.15,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(534,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}IRMÃ CARMEL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:35.16,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seu nome: Irmã Carmel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os céus exigem reconciliação?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles causaram grande medo \Nem todo o mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você não entende?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se os matarem,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:16:03.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,os guerreiros de Elbaf formarão um exército \Npara se vingar do mundo inteiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:05.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Perdoem seus pecados!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:16.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu os guiarei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:24.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para um mundo onde todas as \Nraças possam se dar as mãos...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:28.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e rir juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:35.11,Principio,,0,0,0,,Com o tempo, chamaram Carmel de Mãe \Ne ela abriu um orfanato...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:38.01,Principio,,0,0,0,,...chamado "Casa dos Cordeirinhos", \Nonde aceitava crianças...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:41.29,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,972)}...de qualquer raça ou posição social, \Nque não tinham para onde ir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.08,Principio,,0,0,0,,Aqui, em Elbaf, onde os gigantes vivem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:51.70,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,744)}Enquanto isso, ela trabalhava como a ponte \Nentre humanos e gigantes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:57.00,Principio,,0,0,0,,Trinta e sete anos depois daquilo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe mais, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:17:02.87,OPLetreros,,690,0,380,,{\fs22\fad(250,250)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(1000,370)}MÃE CARMEL \N(80 ANOS DE IDADE) \N E OS FILHOS DA CASA DOS CORDEIROS {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:03.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos viver juntos e felizes \Naté seus pais voltarem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles não vão voltar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:06.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles te abandonaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:10.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Todas as crianças são únicas aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Todos nós fomos abandonados \Npor nossos pais!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Logo você vai se dar bem com eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:21.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou com fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é um gigante?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:26.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos comer então!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.98,Principio,,0,0,0,,Havia um príncipe que foi expulso \Nde seu país após um golpe de estado...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.39,Principio,,0,0,0,,Uma criança prestes a ser escravizada \Ndevido à pobreza...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:37.18,Principio,,0,0,0,,Esses encrenqueiros que nem seus \Npais conseguiram controlar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:43.08,Principio,,0,0,0,,...viviam na vila dos gigantes, \Nindependentemente de sua posição social ou raça.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:47.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela é nova?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:55.90,Principio,,0,0,0,,Principalmente Linlin, que sempre foi \Nmaior que os outros,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.23,Principio,,0,0,0,,se sentia muito à vontade...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:02.78,Principio,,0,0,0,,...em Elbaf, onde as pessoas, \Nas casas e tudo mais...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:05.57,Principio,,0,0,0,,...pela primeira vez eram do seu tamanho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:11.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, que legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.65,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(414,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}NO DIA SEGUINTE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que estranho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que estranho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Opa, opa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Linlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mãe, sabe o que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:32.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um urso e um lobo estavam \Nbrigando na floresta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:36.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como achei que não era bom que brigassem \Ne para que se dessem bem,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:39.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,eu os coloquei na mesma jaula.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:44.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o urso comeu o lobo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então eu bati no urso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece que o urso está muito arrependido.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quantas vezes você bateu nele?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:53.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só uma vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:58.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela matou ele com um golpe só?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:10.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você só queria que eles fossem amigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:13.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin, você é tão doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:20.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, vamos voltar para os outros!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:28.62,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1412)}Para Linlin, Carmel foi a primeira \Npessoa que a entendeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:31.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu vi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:34.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin matou um urso com um golpe só!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:35.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela é perigosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:39.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês ouviram que Eyri-kun, \No gigante, acabou machucado?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:42.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela disse que queria matar o mosquito \Nque pousou nele!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:45.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele quebrou vários ossos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ai, ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:52.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo, Linlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:55.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mãe, socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:20:00.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É que ele tem um cotovelo a mais, \Nentão pensei em tirá-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:03.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, ele é um homem de braços longos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele é assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:07.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:10.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin, o que você está fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:16.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele tem nadadeiras, então \Npensei em tirá-las...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:17.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os homens-peixe têm algumas \Ncaracterísticas de peixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:23.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:27.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Perdoem ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:38.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin é muito bondosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:46.72,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,742)}Carmel perdoou tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:49.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esperem, esperem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin vai me matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:57.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esperem, esperem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:00.79,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dez meses depois, em Elbaf, o país \Nbelicoso do Novo Mundo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:59.42,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(414,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}KASHII
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:05.57,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\an8}os guerreiros haviam aceitado \NLinlin de braços abertos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.38,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(414,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}OIMO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esperem, esperem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:11.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já vai fazer quarenta anos...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:16.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,746)}Já houve algum duelo \Nque durou tanto tempo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:18.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,700)}Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:21.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver daqui a dez anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já se prepararam?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kashii, preparar para quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:37.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, Linlin-chan, é sua primeira vez, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:42.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Em Elbaf, jejuamos por doze dias \Nantes do festival do solstício de inverno!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Jejuar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ou seja, não comer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:48.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só podemos beber água.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:51.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por doze dias a partir \Nde amanhã, entendeu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:55.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou ficar com fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:58.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas se você aguentar, terá um festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lute contra si mesmo, Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:10.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Levante-se, Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:21.06,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(414,1164)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}HAJRUDIN
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:20.13,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Este jovem gigante, Hajrudin,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:23.76,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mais tarde encontrou \NLuffy em Dressrosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:27.73,Principio,,0,0,0,,se encantou com sua determinação e, \Njunto com Bartolomeo e os outros,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.73,0:22:30.20,Principio,,0,0,0,,bebeu uma taça de saquê \Npara se tornar seu subordinado.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:35.98,Principio,,0,0,0,,Agora ele é um membro da \NFrota dos Chapéus de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:39.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O encrenqueiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:44.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sem dúvida, algum dos chefes, \NDorry ou Brogy, voltará,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:47.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,e os Piratas Gigantes renascerão!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:49.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é um guerreiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:51.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Continue treinando, Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:51.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:55.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gosto desse espírito!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:56.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rydin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:22:57.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:07.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Barbacascada-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:09.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Barbamontanha-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:13.82,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(624,436)\fad(500,369)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}JARUL\N"BARBAMONTAÑA"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:13.82,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(987,432)\fad(500,369)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}JORUL\N"BARBACASCADA"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:13.82,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(617,691)\fad(500,369)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}345 ANOS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:13.82,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(992,684)\fad(500,369)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}344 ANOS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:13.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Carmel diz que é melhor negociar \Ndo que roubar, e isso é bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:17.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mas não vamos esquecer que somos guerreiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:19.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:22.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Jarul-sama e Jorul-sama são incríveis!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:26.21,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(665,404)\fad(522,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}EX-CAPITÃES DOS PIRATAS GIGANTES\NOS GUERREIROS MAIS VELHOS DO MUNDO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:26.21,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,720)\fad(522,0)\bord2.0\fscx140\fscy140}HERÓIS DOS GIGANTES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:26.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eles são guerreiros respeitados \Npor todos os gigantes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:30.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um dia serei assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:33.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que os traz aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.13,0:23:38.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos comer semla na vila, então viemos \Nbuscar as crianças da Casa dos Cordeirinhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:41.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem na hora, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:43.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que é semla?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:45.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É um doce delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.33,0:23:46.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hã? Um doce?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:50.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Antes do jejum, nos alimentamos \Nbem comendo semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.48,0:23:53.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos comer agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:55.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse doce?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:24:00.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É creme batido colocado entre duas \Ncamadas de pão doce que contém maçapão...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:02.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...com açúcar polvilhado por cima!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:04.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É a iguaria antes do jejum!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:07.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:12.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:16.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pelo nascimento do \NPríncipe Loki no castelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.32,0:24:21.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E por Rodo e Goldberg, \Nque nasceram na vila!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:25.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agradecemos ao sol pelo \Ncrescimento de nossos filhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:26.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:26.91,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.91,0:24:29.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bom apetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.91,0:24:29.65,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Bom apetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:30.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.68,0:24:31.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.57,0:24:33.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Temos muitos, então \Ncomam à vontade!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:39.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,D-Do...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.40,0:24:42.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Doce demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.12,0:24:44.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:46.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que felicidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.06,0:24:52.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso, delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.62,0:24:53.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Doce, doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.70,0:24:54.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso, delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.80,0:24:56.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso, delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.42,0:25:04.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso, delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.06,0:25:04.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.68,0:25:06.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.01,0:25:07.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não coma tão rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.86,0:25:09.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você vai acabar com tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.66,0:25:12.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se esqueça de agradecer ao sol!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.83,0:25:16.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.16,0:25:21.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.10,0:25:22.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.64,0:25:25.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.29,0:25:32.29,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,473)\fad(522,440)\bord2.0\fscx150\fscy150}TERCEIRO DIA DE JEJUM
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.19,0:25:30.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{\an8}Mãe...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.34,0:25:32.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vou morrer de fome...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.55,0:25:36.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O festival do solstício de inverno \Ncelebra a morte e ressurreição do sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.86,0:25:42.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O sol voltará a brilhar intensamente \Napós superar o inverno rigoroso.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.92,0:25:45.31,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,473)\fad(522,0)\bord2.0\fscx150\fscy150}QUARTO DIA DE JEJUM
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.31,0:25:50.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quanto mais você sofre, mais agradece ao sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.23,0:25:52.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, vamos nos esforçar!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.38,0:26:01.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se Mãe diz, eu vou me esforçar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.37,0:26:05.87,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,473)\fad(522,0)\bord2.0\fscx150\fscy150}QUINTO DIA DE JEJUM
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.11,0:26:08.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Perdi peso...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.50,0:26:10.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não mudou nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.04,0:26:11.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você acha?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.56,0:26:13.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que estranho...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.05,0:26:14.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.84,0:26:16.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está se esforçando!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.54,0:26:17.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já está quase lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.06,0:26:20.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.45,0:26:23.76,Principio,,0,0,0,,Linlin começou a amar muito a Mãe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.14,0:26:26.64,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,473)\fad(522,0)\bord2.0\fscx150\fscy150}SEXTO DIA DE JEJUM
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.71,0:26:30.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Semla é delicioso...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.66,0:26:33.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu quero...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.32,0:26:39.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,972)}...comer de novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.20,0:26:45.70,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,473)\fad(522,0)\bord2.0\fscx150\fscy150}SÉTIMO DIA DE JEJUM
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.92,0:26:50.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.30,0:26:54.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mãe, socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.62,0:26:58.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Gerd?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.13,0:27:01.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.01,0:27:10.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.01,0:27:16.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.34,0:27:17.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que ela fez?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.30,0:27:19.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.24,0:27:22.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me tragam semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.95,0:27:26.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.95,0:27:32.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin destruiu a vila de Elbaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.86,0:27:34.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É um pesadelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.13,0:27:39.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você se atreveu a fazer isso, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.82,0:27:42.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não tem o direito \Nde agradecer ao sol!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.34,0:27:45.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo sendo uma criança, \Nisso é imperdoável!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.68,0:27:46.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Jorul-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.97,0:27:49.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Semla... Semla...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.93,0:27:51.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Carmel...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.48,0:27:52.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.76,0:27:55.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo parecendo uma criança...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.52,0:27:57.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, Jorul-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.36,0:27:59.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela é um demônio!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.82,0:28:12.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}Semla...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.58,0:28:15.60,Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição de vídeo:\N Feeso,\NGalaxy 9000\N\NTempos:\NKaitouYahiko,\NUmim\N\NControle de qualidade:\NNAGATEI,\NFeeso,\NGalaxy 9000,\NGrug,\NPepperjack\N\NEdição de áudio:\N Halee\N\NLegendas:\NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\NRAFAEL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.65,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.49,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.86,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.07,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:28.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A alegria de nossos corações colidindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:35.76,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...e a tristeza ao secar as lágrimas de alegria...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:43.35,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...conecte-as e agite-as...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:50.23,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...no topo deste vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.19,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você parou de buscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.57,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que continua lutando sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.87,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ei, para qual futuro você se preparou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.37,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Você já realizou seu sonho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.38,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:11.00,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:14.22,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.55,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços imutáveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.85,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nos confins deste enorme mundo azul,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.89,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}há um lugar onde quero ir com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.64,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se há uma rota para chegar lá,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:33.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}já decidimos há muito tempo.
